<paragraph blockId="2.[151,603,1012,1039]" box="[151,603,1012,1039]" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">
<heading bold="true" box="[151,603,1012,1039]" fontSize="11" level="1" pageId="2" pageNumber="127" reason="1">
<taxonomicName authority="C. L. Koch, 1836" authorityName="C. L. Koch" authorityYear="1836" box="[151,603,1012,1039]" class="Chilopoda" family="Scolopendridae" genus="Scolopendra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scolopendromorpha" pageId="2" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="italica">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,603,1012,1039]" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,385,1012,1039]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">Scolopendra italica</emphasis>
C. L. Koch, 1836
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="127" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,1081,1349]" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">
The name 
<taxonomicName authority="C. L Koch, 1836" authorityName="C. L. Koch" authorityYear="1836" box="[267,674,1081,1108]" class="Chilopoda" family="Scolopendridae" genus="Scolopendra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scolopendromorpha" pageId="2" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="italica">
<emphasis box="[267,486,1081,1107]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">Scolopendra italica</emphasis>
C. L Koch, 1836
</taxonomicName>
is depicted with the corrected date “1836” instead of the widely used date “1837”. 
<bibRefCitation author="Gervais, P." box="[303,474,1115,1142]" pageId="2" pageNumber="127" pagination="35 - 60" refId="ref6440" refString="Gervais, P. (1837) Etude pour servir a l'histoire naturelle des Myriapodes. Annales des Sciences naturelles. Zoologie, 2 (7), 35 - 60. [published August 1837]" type="journal article" year="1837">Gervais (1837)</bibRefCitation>
seems to be the first author who cited the original description of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="C. L. Koch" authorityYear="1836" box="[1227,1328,1115,1142]" class="Chilopoda" family="Scolopendridae" genus="Scolopendra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scolopendromorpha" pageId="2" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="italica">
<emphasis box="[1227,1328,1115,1142]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">S. italica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
correctly (in Koch, Deutschl., Crust., Myr., Arach., 
<emphasis box="[620,668,1150,1176]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">Heft</emphasis>
9, species no. 1), although without date. The correct reference of the original description was also given by Koch himself (
<bibRefCitation author="Koch, C. L. &amp; Kritische Revision der Insectenfaune Deutschlands von Dr" box="[744,870,1184,1210]" pageId="2" pageNumber="127" pagination="1 - 190" refId="ref6685" refString="Koch, C. L. (1847) Kritische Revision der Insectenfaune Deutschlands von Dr. Panzer and Dr. Herrich-Schaffer, Heft 1 - 190. III. Bandchen, enthaltend die Verzeichnisse und Berichtigungen zu Deutschlands Crustaceen, Myriapoden und Arachniden und ein System der Myriapoden von C. L. Koch [additional title page: System der Myriapoden mit den Verzeichnissen und Berichtigungen zu Deutschlands Crustaceen, Myriapoden und Arachniden. Heft 1 - 40. von C. L. Koch)]. Pustet, Regensburg, 272 pp., 10 pls. [date on title page: 1847, date of preface: 1 April 1846, in the text referred to as &quot; System der Myriapoda &quot;] https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 49866" type="book chapter" year="1847">Koch 1847</bibRefCitation>
) with equal ranking of both 
<emphasis box="[1185,1246,1184,1210]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">Hefte</emphasis>
as “9. (142.) 1.”, and 
<bibRefCitation author="Koch, C. L." box="[199,355,1219,1245]" pageId="2" pageNumber="127" refId="ref6877" refString="Koch, C. L. (1863 b) Die Myriapoden: getreu nach der Natur abgebildet und beschrieben. Band 2. H. W. Schmidt, Regensburg, 112 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 10639" type="book" year="1863">Koch (1863b)</bibRefCitation>
as “Deutschl. Crustaceen, Arachniden und Myriapoden Heft 9”, neither of them dated.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,1081,1349]" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">
The date “1836” together with the reference to 
<emphasis box="[718,766,1253,1279]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">Heft</emphasis>
9 of the Koch series was only used recently (
<date box="[1267,1389,1253,1279]" pageId="2" pageNumber="127" value="2021-02-01">1 Feb 2021</date>
) for the Zoobank record (http://zoobank.org/NomenclaturalActs/3c684667-fc35-4942-bbe9-d2462fb1d5f8, and http:// zoobank.org/References/3e59cf22-15c6-49d4-9724-f9692847f2f1) last accessed in 23 
<superScript attach="left" box="[1116,1129,1322,1336]" fontSize="6" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">th</superScript>
january of 2022).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,1391,1485]" box="[151,384,1391,1417]" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">Original description:</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,1391,1485]" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">
Similar to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="C. L. Koch" authorityYear="1836" box="[321,442,1425,1451]" class="Chilopoda" family="Scolopendridae" genus="Scolopendra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scolopendromorpha" pageId="2" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="clavipes">
<emphasis box="[321,442,1425,1451]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">S. clavipes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(see reasoning above), 
<taxonomicName authorityName="C. L. Koch" authorityYear="1836" box="[714,815,1425,1451]" class="Chilopoda" family="Scolopendridae" genus="Scolopendra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scolopendromorpha" pageId="2" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="italica">
<emphasis box="[714,815,1425,1451]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">S. italica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was originally described on 1 
<superScript attach="left" box="[1160,1171,1425,1439]" fontSize="6" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">st</superScript>
October in Koch C. L. (1836a) (precedence), and, simultaneously, in 
<bibRefCitation author="Koch, C. L." box="[669,825,1459,1485]" pageId="2" pageNumber="127" refId="ref6618" refString="Koch, C. L. (1836 b) Deutschlands Crustaceen, Myriapoden und Arachniden. Ein Beitrag zur deutschen Fauna. Herausgegeben von Dr. Herrich-Schaffer. 9 tes Heft. F. Pustet, Regensburg, 90 pp. [Author of text and illustrations; the series referred to in the present text as &quot; Koch series &quot;; published 1 October]" type="book" year="1836">Koch (1836b)</bibRefCitation>
(subordinated).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[197,1405,1528,1692]" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">
<taxonomicName authority="C. L Koch., 1836" authorityName="C. L. Koch" authorityYear="1836" box="[197,619,1528,1555]" class="Chilopoda" family="Scolopendridae" genus="Scolopendra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scolopendromorpha" pageId="2" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="italica">
<emphasis box="[197,417,1528,1554]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">Scolopendra italica</emphasis>
C. L Koch., 1836
</taxonomicName>
[1 Oct.]. Index 
<emphasis box="[798,868,1528,1554]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">Tab. 1</emphasis>
, Plate 9.1., Text headed 9.1 [2 pp., second page unpaginated] – In: Koch, C.L. (1836a). Deutschlands Crustaceen, Myriapoden und Arachniden. Ein Beitrag zur deutschen Fauna. [Herausgegeben von Dr. Herrich-Schäffer] [N.B.: This statement “Edited by Dr. Herrich-Schäffer“ is true for the whole Koch series, however printed only on some title pages]. 9 
<emphasis box="[1272,1360,1632,1658]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">tes Heft</emphasis>
, 24 plates and associated letterpress. Regensburg: Fr. Pustet.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,1735,2038]" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">
The differences between the parallel published, corresponding 
<emphasis box="[892,953,1735,1761]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">Hefte</emphasis>
of the Koch series and the Herrich-Schäffer series were described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Nagel, P. &amp; Grieder, L." box="[433,696,1769,1795]" pageId="2" pageNumber="127" pagination="1 - 156" refId="ref7343" refString="Nagel, P. &amp; Grieder, L. (2019) Herrich-Schaffer's Deutschlands Insecten ... (1829 - 1844), the associate publication of Koch's Deutschlands Crustaceen ... (1835 - 1844), and Heft 110 (1823) of Panzer's Faunae Insectorum Germanicae ...: bibliographic notes and dating. Sherbornia, 5 (1), 1 - 156." type="journal article" year="2019">Nagel &amp; Grieder (2019</bibRefCitation>
, p. 39). They are also present between 
<emphasis box="[1132,1180,1769,1795]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">Heft</emphasis>
9 and 142.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,1735,2038]" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">
The currently accepted (valid) name for 
<taxonomicName authority="C. L. Koch, 1836" authorityName="C. L. Koch" authorityYear="1836" box="[661,970,1803,1830]" class="Chilopoda" family="Scolopendridae" genus="Scolopendra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scolopendromorpha" pageId="2" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="italica">
<emphasis box="[661,762,1803,1830]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">S. italica</emphasis>
C. L. Koch, 1836
</taxonomicName>
is 
<taxonomicName authority="Latreille, 1829" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1829" box="[1005,1436,1803,1830]" class="Chilopoda" family="Scolopendridae" genus="Scolopendra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scolopendromorpha" pageId="2" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cingulata">
<emphasis box="[1005,1262,1803,1829]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">Scolopendra cingulata</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Latreille, M." box="[1270,1436,1803,1830]" pageId="2" pageNumber="127" pagination="326 - 339" refId="ref7031" refString="Latreille, M. (1829) Les Myriapodes. In: Cuvier, P. M. L., Le regne animal distribue d'apres son organisation. Nouvelle Edition, Revue et Augmentee. Tome IV. Crustaces, Arachnides et Partie des Insectes. Deterville, Paris, pp. 326 - 339." type="book chapter" year="1829">Latreille, 1829</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(see Bonato 
<emphasis box="[298,358,1838,1864]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">et al.</emphasis>
2016, founded on 
<bibRefCitation author="Newport, G." box="[583,751,1838,1865]" pageId="2" pageNumber="127" pagination="265 - 302" refId="ref7476" refString="Newport, G. (1845) Monograph of the class Myriapoda order Chilopoda; with observations on the general arrangement of the Articulata. Transactions of the Linnean Society of London, 19 (26), 265 - 302 + 349 - 439. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1096 - 3642.1842. tb 00370. x" type="journal article" year="1845">Newport 1845</bibRefCitation>
, p. 388, see also 
<uri pageId="2" pageNumber="127">
urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act: 
<uuid pageId="2" pageNumber="127">3C684667-FC35- 4942-BBE9-D2462FB1D5F8</uuid>
</uri>
, http://zoobank.org/NomenclaturalActs/3c684667-fc35-4942-bbe9-d2462fb1d5f8; last accessed 
<date box="[309,469,1906,1933]" pageId="2" pageNumber="127" value="2022-01-16">
16 
<superScript attach="left" box="[337,350,1906,1920]" fontSize="6" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">th</superScript>
Jan. 2022
</date>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,1735,2038]" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">
The often referenced date “1837” traces back to 
<bibRefCitation author="Kraepelin, K." box="[747,941,1941,1967]" pageId="2" pageNumber="127" pagination="1 - 276" refId="ref7003" refString="Kraepelin, K. (1903) Revision der Scolopendriden. Mitteilungen aus dem Naturhistorischen Museum in Hamburg, 20 (2), 1 - 276." type="journal article" year="1903">Kraepelin (1903)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Attems, C. G." box="[952,1115,1941,1967]" pageId="2" pageNumber="127" pagination="2" refId="ref6130" refString="Attems, C. G. (1930) Myriopoda. 2. Scolopendromorpha. In: Schulze, F. E. &amp; Kukenthal, W. (Eds.), Das Tierreich. Vol. 54. Walter de Gruyter &amp; Co., Berlin and Leipzig, pp. 1 - 308." type="book chapter" year="1930">Attems (1930)</bibRefCitation>
or even earlier to the wrong dating of 
<emphasis box="[263,311,1976,2002]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">Heft</emphasis>
9 of the Koch series. Bonato 
<emphasis box="[659,710,1975,2001]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">et al</emphasis>
. (2016), item “ 
<taxonomicName authority="C. L. Koch, 1837" authorityName="C. L. Koch" authorityYear="1837" box="[888,1325,1975,2002]" class="Chilopoda" family="Scolopendridae" genus="Scolopendra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scolopendromorpha" pageId="2" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="italica">
<emphasis box="[888,1111,1975,2001]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">Scolopendra italica</emphasis>
C. L. Koch, 1837
</taxonomicName>
”, mix the references of 
<emphasis box="[304,352,2012,2038]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">Heft</emphasis>
9 of the Koch series and 
<emphasis box="[637,685,2012,2038]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="127">Heft</emphasis>
142 of the Herrich-Schäffer series, and also cite “1837” in error.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
